        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Recommended Roadmap\n",
        "\n",
        "<div class=\"roadmap\">\n",
        "<div class=\"roadmap-item\">\n",
        "  <div class=\"roadmap-title\">C3 — Analyst Escalation Queue</div>\n",
        "  <div class=\"roadmap-desc\">Capture near-misses (score 0.20–0.30) with a UI-only change. Zero risk to existing recognition. Builds a corpus of analyst decisions that calibrates every other solution.</div>\n",
        "</div>\n",
        "<div class=\"roadmap-item\">\n",
        "  <div class=\"roadmap-title\">C1 — Widen LOG_EPS to 0.40</div>\n",
        "  <div class=\"roadmap-desc\">Evaluate on a hold-out set. If false-positive rate is acceptable, deploy globally. Recovers a large fraction of the out-of-range population automatically with a single config change.</div>\n",
        "</div>\n",
        "<div class=\"roadmap-item\">\n",
        "  <div class=\"roadmap-title\">B — Similar-Product Transfer</div>\n",
        "  <div class=\"roadmap-desc\">Co-design similarity criteria with domain analysts. Pilot on one manufacturer/category before expanding. Borrow ThresholdV2 profiles from structurally similar products with rich history.</div>\n",
        "</div>\n",
        "<div class=\"roadmap-item\">\n",
        "  <div class=\"roadmap-title\">A — Agentic Web Search</div>\n",
        "  <div class=\"roadmap-desc\">Prototype on a small batch of zero-history products. Evaluate citation quality and build the analyst review workflow. Requires prompt engineering, de-duplication, and a write-back feedback loop before scaling.</div>\n",
        "</div>\n",
        "</div>\n",
        "\n",
